name: *1* The Tree of BLUEM
description:
The origin tree of this new series, "The Trees". There will be many more trees. 

Marked by this piece, my hope with this series is to grow a network, a resource, and an appreciation for trees, nature, and environmental advocacy. How? That is still in development. Though, this is the seed of a beautiful forest of hope and art. Blooming. @bluemNFT
